  "description": "Rearrangement of wet spaces internally (i.e. the relocation of kitchen, WC and utility room facilities) as well as various strip out works to modern fixtures and finishes. Removal of modern bi-fold doors. Replacement of floor finishes. Installation of built-in joinery including shelves, wardrobes and timber shutters (front window only). Installation of fire/smoke detectors. Replacement of wiring and surface mounted sockets on skirtings. These works were carried out in 2016-17. Replacement of flat roof finishes and flashings and new coping stones. New insulation to ceiling void. These works were carried out in 2020. New kitchen door. Like-for-like replacement of kitchen timber casement window. Redecoration of rendered front facade like-for-like, repairs to front railings including reinstatement of missing finials, investigation works to front entrance steps. Installation of mechnical ventilation and duct work including adapting exisitng chimney flue. Reducing height of built in wardrobe. New lime plaster applied directly to brickwork of exposed chimney breast. These works have not commenced.",
